				Bill 148, shall remain operative only until the operative date of this bill, at which time Section 2.5 of this bill shall become operative, and Section 2 of this bill shall not become operative.</div></div></div><div id="s70.13998392708788843"><div><div style="margin:0 0 1em 0;"><h3 style="font-weight:bold; display:inline;">SEC. 6</h3> If the Commission on State Mandates determines that this act contains costs mandated by the state, reimbursement to local agencies and school districts for those costs shall be made pursuant to Part 7 (commencing with Section 17500) of Division 4 of Title 2 of the Government Code.</div></div></div></div></div></body></html>
